### Test Password Reset Flow

# 1. Send OTP for password reset
POST https://api.festiveguest.com/api/email/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "purpose": "password-reset"
}

### 

# 2. Reset password with OTP
POST https://api.festiveguest.com/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "otpCode": "123456",
  "newPassword": "newPassword123"
}

###

# 3. Change password (requires authentication)
POST https://api.festiveguest.com/api/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "currentPassword": "oldPassword123",
  "newPassword": "newPassword456"
}

